INSERT INTO `leads` VALUES (1,'204414557','https://www.odesk.com/jobs/LAMP-Expert_%7E01d5d2fae8498f53e0?source=rss','LAMP Expert - oDesk','We are looking for a developer that is comfortable with all aspects of Using LAMP.<br />\n<br />\nKnowing PHP MYSQL and Apache is important also having some Linux Administration (Red Hat) is also important <br />\n<br />\nwe have a website that was built suing plain PHP (no frameworks) and we also need the person to be able to understand and work with bootstrap.<br /><br /><b>Posted On</b>: August 18, 2014 10:11 UTC<br /><b>ID</b>: 204414557<br /><b>Category</b>: Web Development &gt; Web Programming<br /><b>Skills</b>: Array, Array, Array, Array, Array, Array, Array, Array, Array<br /><b>Country</b>: United States<br /><a href=\"https://www.odesk.com/jobs/LAMP-Expert_%7E01d5d2fae8498f53e0?source=rss\">click to apply</a>',0.00,'','August 18, 2014 10:11 UTC',2,0,'Mon, 18 Aug 2014 10:11:43 +0000',1,5,'',1,0,0,1,1408626537,0),(2,'204414547','https://www.odesk.com/jobs/Need-assistant-for-various-complex-projects_%7E016586846d737bd93d?source=rss','Need an assistant for various complex projects. - oDesk','Need a web developer. Having good knowledge of core php(must), wordpress, joomla. Who is flexible to work in day and night shifts.<br />\n<br />\nIf you are ready for a test only then apply.<br />\n<br />\nhrly price must be 2usd or less than that. If you are looking for higher prices then please don&#039;t apply.<br /><br /><b>Posted On</b>: August 18, 2014 10:09 UTC<br /><b>ID</b>: 204414547<br /><b>Category</b>: Web Development &gt; Web Programming<br /><b>Skills</b>: Array, Array, Array, Array, Array, Array, Array<br /><b>Country</b>: India<br /><a href=\"https://www.odesk.com/jobs/Need-assistant-for-various-complex-projects_%7E016586846d737bd93d?source=rss\">click to apply</a>',0.00,'','August 18, 2014 10:09 UTC',2,0,'Mon, 18 Aug 2014 10:09:36 +0000',1,5,'',1,0,0,1,1408619598,0),(3,'204414538','https://www.odesk.com/jobs/Opencart-Responsive-Theme-CSS-Changes_%7E016fae45a64e99370c?source=rss','Opencart - Responsive Theme - CSS Changes - oDesk','Hi<br />\n<br />\nThis is my website - <a href=\"https://www.odesk.com/leaving-odesk?ref=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.fashionablehijabs.co.uk%2F\" title=\"You are about to go to a URL outside odesk.com\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.fashionablehijabs.co.uk/</a><br />\n<br />\nOn the PC version <br />\nAt the top I want Facebook and Instagram images adding (which links back to FB and IG).<br />\n<br />\nOn the mobile version<br />\n - At the top I want Facebook and Instagram images adding (which links back to FB and IG).<br />\n- The cart total over laps the logo, this needs fixing<br />\n- The menu navigation needs moving down and made more visible<br />\n- I want the product image slightly bigger and have the image, title and price centre aligned<br />\n- On the blog page the seach bar is not aligned correctly this needs fixing.<br />\n<br />\nIf you look at the mobile site for <a href=\"https://www.odesk.com/leaving-odesk?ref=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hijabjunkie.com.\" title=\"You are about to go to a URL outside odesk.com\" target=\"_blank\">www.hijabjunkie.com.</a> I want all the above to look the same as there&#039;s.<br />\n<br />\nThanks<br /><br /><b>Budget</b>: $25<br /><b>Posted On</b>: August 18, 2014 10:07 UTC<br /><b>ID</b>: 204414538<br /><b>Category</b>: Web Development &gt; Web Design<br /><b>Skills</b>: Array, Array, Array, Array, Array, Array<br /><b>Country</b>: United Kingdom<br /><a href=\"https://www.odesk.com/jobs/Opencart-Responsive-Theme-CSS-Changes_%7E016fae45a64e99370c?source=rss\">click to apply</a>',25.00,'$25','August 18, 2014 10:07 UTC',3,0,'Mon, 18 Aug 2014 10:07:50 +0000',1,5,'',1,0,0,1,1408609023,0),(4,'204414528','https://www.odesk.com/jobs/Multi-homing-configuration-virtual-machine-esxi-vmware_%7E019dca6bf28ade55dc?source=rss','Multi-homing configuration on a virtual machine esxi vmware - oDesk','We have OVH servers.<br />\nOur servers are managed thanks to VMware vcenter.<br />\nFor one VM on one server working with Centos 6, we need to configure multi ips for one magento site. Each ip corresponds to a domain managed by the same magento back end. The problem is that OVH only supports one configuration. Our main ip is working but the other ips are not working with the configuration provided by OVH. We tried other configurations but we received email from OVH which blocked the ips (too much ARP requests on network). We must find a solution to get them working knowing that WHM is installed on this server but we almost dont use it (except for easy apache).<br />\nIps are well configured in vmware (one mac for one ip, one nic one ip).<br />\nYou can find details in French here : <a href=\"https://www.odesk.com/leaving-odesk?ref=http%3A%2F%2Fforum.ovh.com%2Fshowthread.php%3F99347-Probl%25E8me-configuration-ip-multiples-sur-une-vm-esxi\" title=\"You are about to go to a URL outside odesk.com\" target=\"_blank\">http://forum.ovh.com/showthread.php?99347-Probl%E8me-configuration-ip-multiples-sur-une-vm-esxi</a>.<br />\nThanks<br /><br /><b>Posted On</b>: August 18, 2014 10:05 UTC<br /><b>ID</b>: 204414528<br /><b>Category</b>: Networking & Information Systems &gt; Network Administration<br /><b>Skills</b>: Array, Array, Array<br /><b>Country</b>: <br /><a href=\"https://www.odesk.com/jobs/Multi-homing-configuration-virtual-machine-esxi-vmware_%7E019dca6bf28ade55dc?source=rss\">click to apply</a>',0.00,'','August 18, 2014 10:05 UTC',5,0,'Mon, 18 Aug 2014 10:05:44 +0000',1,3,'',1,0,0,1,1408607664,0),(5,'204414491','https://www.odesk.com/jobs/Museumtickets_%7E017bb48fa915573537?source=rss','Museumtickets - oDesk','Work to be done:<br />\nRegistration-user name and password with email verification<br />\nAdded different user identity e.g. administrator, staff<br />\nThe museum should have access to a form to enter the information to be published online [museumtickets.nl]<br />\nWhen the form is send we should